{"tid":1925162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[海外黃店]   台灣抗爭食堂「保護傘」明試業 助流亡手足自食其力","createTime":"2020-03-14T07:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T10:56:34.000Z","uid":28202,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8a9523e3292b6a9cc44be0260c35f4e2009d73","tid":1925162,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"保護傘網址<a href=\"https://achkltd.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fachkltd.com%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=0435bb0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://achkltd.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200311/M5V2OCVT6PU5XH4ZHFVJB77REA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2FM5V2OCVT6PU5XH4ZHFVJB77REA%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=11de0694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2FM5V2OCVT6PU5XH4ZHFVJB77REA%2F&h=0a8aec1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200311/M5V2OCVT6PU5XH4ZHFVJB77REA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200311/large/1583904502_fc41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583904502_fc41.jpg&h=f9100324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批年輕抗爭者因為參與反送中運動流亡台灣，但伴隨長期逗留衍生的生活問題需要解決。律師兼區議員黃國桐早前發起「保護傘」計劃，希望在台灣開店讓手足自食其力。籌備數月，首間「抗爭食堂」的內部裝修及招牌都準備就緒，明日起開始試業。<br />\n<br />\n據悉店址位於台北新生南路，鄰近國立臺灣大學。據Telegram流傳的店舖相片，金黃色的招牌襯黑色書法風格「保護傘」三隻大字，在平凡的街道上相當凸出搶眼。而根據「保護傘」Facebook專頁，上周新店內部裝修及廚具用品等已經完成，附近則另設住宿設施供手足居住，以便工作和讀書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃國桐接受查詢時僅稱新店明日起開始試業，包括菜單等細節仍未有最終定案，亦未有透露人手及日後營運計劃等內容。被問到店舖開設在臺大學區附近，會否擔心太過張揚引來不必要麻煩，他指台灣是民主法治之區，手足全部都同意光明正大做事。<br />\n<br />\n另外，保護傘亦已開設網店，所有貨品均在外國或台灣製造及生產，扣除成本全數用作支持保護傘其他各項目之用"},{"pid":"9e604dbc9a2f355d11d90a35edf1721d2218e6fe","tid":1925162,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b716e5e2fad75dbb3efa15562667ce5b3e320a63","tid":1925162,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b5fb8a4a46c99637d74ef440e6c2b81cb147368","tid":1925162,"uid":266084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:02:15.000Z","msg":"咁快就有五毛出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67085b281f884c671a444ae178708f5b9c75b512","tid":1925162,"uid":72398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d913e129a1507041ebf309546c1c675585ff08a6","tid":1925162,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕推一下"},{"pid":"a30207c0ed3650929d933f22059fca796caf6814","tid":1925162,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxUT0MY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxUT0MY.jpg&h=3edea54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eg2Kn0j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feg2Kn0j.jpg&h=830ff7c8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}